IEnumeratorWrapper
[LuaRegister]
public
IEnumeratorWrapper

Wraps an IEnumerator<object> to make it compatible with the Lua environment. Instances of this class can be created and used within Lua scripts.

Properties
Enumerator
public IEnumerator<object> Enumerator { get }

The IEnumerator<object> that this wrapper is wrapping.
